                <p class="contentp">
                    The Brampton campus is the latest chapter in the Medix College success book. Located at 499 Main

                    Street inside Shoppers World Brampton, this campus has grown rapidly and has proudly educated

                    students to thrive in the healthcare industry. The campus boasts modern facilities, fully equipped with

                    the latest technology to provide an excellent learning and teaching environment.

                    <br /><br />

                    The Brampton campus faculty consists of over twenty professional, experienced members who are

                    committed to fulfilling the school’s mission: “To service with excellence the needs of our community

                    and the needs of our graduates by matching skills.” With the addition of North American Trade

                    Schools (NATS) to the Career College Group campus, we are now able to meet demand for both

                    Healthcare and Skilled Trades graduates.
